559
00:36:26,460 --> 00:36:28,519
The one I use for VIPs.

560
00:36:28,860 --> 00:36:30,130
It's phone number 10.

561
00:36:30,130 --> 00:36:31,960
The one you use for people
you don't want to talk to.

562
00:36:33,329 --> 00:36:34,400
Who is it?

563
00:36:34,630 --> 00:36:35,929
It's President Sim Hae Yong.

564
00:36:41,369 --> 00:36:43,440
Veronica Park speaking.

565
00:36:43,639 --> 00:36:46,480
You'll get a call soon regarding the
extraordinary stockholders' meeting.

566
00:36:47,610 --> 00:36:50,210
I'm hoping you'll attend this one.

567
00:36:51,610 --> 00:36:52,949
No.

568
