573
00:37:09,469 --> 00:37:12,469
Did he tell you that things are
going well between us?

574
00:37:12,900 --> 00:37:14,699
Well... Well, yes.

575
00:37:15,269 --> 00:37:16,440
What is he thinking?

576
00:37:16,440 --> 00:37:20,039
You should drop by
to say hello to him.

577
00:37:20,739 --> 00:37:22,650
It'd be even better
if you write me a POA.

578
00:37:24,010 --> 00:37:26,820
President Park, it's the number
you've been waiting for, 6421!

579
00:37:26,820 --> 00:37:28,820
Awesome! I need to hang up.

580
00:37:33,789 --> 00:37:35,659
Veronica Park speaking.

581
00:37:36,389 --> 00:37:39,599
I don't know this number.
May I ask who's calling?

582
00:37:41,099 --> 00:37:42,199
It's me, Gi Dae Ju.

583
00:37:42,869 --> 00:37:44,400
Can we meet today?

584
00:37:47,239 --> 00:37:50,340
I've never been
inside a hotel suite before.

585
00:37:50,469 --> 00:37:53,739
