in a six-star hotel suite.

586
00:37:53,980 --> 00:37:55,610
But did you really have to bring
that rice cooker...

587
00:37:55,610 --> 00:37:57,079
and ruin the interior?

588
00:37:57,809 --> 00:38:01,219
There's a hotel buffet here
that you love more than yourself.

589
00:38:01,380 --> 00:38:04,590
Of course I made sure to bring
elastic waist pants for the buffet.

590
00:38:04,719 --> 00:38:06,460
But I can't always have buffet...

591
00:38:06,460 --> 00:38:08,119
until the stockholders' meeting.

592
00:38:08,119 --> 00:38:09,389
It's really expensive.

593
00:38:11,929 --> 00:38:13,599
