594
00:38:14,530 --> 00:38:15,599
USB?

595
00:38:15,800 --> 00:38:18,400
Remember the suit you wore
on the day of the accident?

596
00:38:18,400 --> 00:38:19,900
I found it in that suit.

597
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:23,010
What are you talking about?
I brought it from Dae Ju's place.

598
00:38:23,670 --> 00:38:25,440
What? That can't be right.

599
00:38:26,809 --> 00:38:28,940
I'm sure it was in the paper bag.

600
00:38:31,780 --> 00:38:33,820
Here we are. The hotel suite.

601
00:38:48,199 --> 00:38:50,070
What should I do with the car?

602
00:38:51,269 --> 00:38:53,739
You won't have to come here
for a while.

603
00:38:53,739 --> 00:38:55,809
Director Do will be staying here
for a couple of days.

604
00:38:55,869 --> 00:38:59,139
Then I'll drive you home.

605
00:38:59,710 --> 00:39:01,539
No, it's okay.
Why would you do that?

606
00:39:02,280 --> 00:39:03,280
Well...

607
00:39:03,880 --> 00:39:06,650
You guys are working so hard.
Let me do anything to help.

608
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:10,820
I'll drive you home safely.

609
00:39:18,690 --> 00:39:20,429
Where should I begin?

610
00:39:20,860 --> 00:39:23,699
If I start with sales,
it might seem a little arrogant.

611
00:39:24,599 --> 00:39:26,699
Would it be too obvious
if you started out with an apology?

612
00:39:28,699 --> 00:39:30,809
I wonder what she would've done.

613
00:39:32,739 --> 00:39:33,780
Who?

614
00:39:37,079 --> 00:39:39,550
Are you talking about Veronica Park?

615
00:39:41,380 --> 00:39:44,789
She's probably more experienced
with stuff like this than I am.

616
00:39:50,559 --> 00:39:53,429
Why do you like her, Director Do?

617
00:39:54,230 --> 00:39:55,300
Me?

618
00:39:56,829 --> 00:39:59,670
Why do you think I like her?

619
00:40:01,239 --> 00:40:04,469
Do you really think
your boss is someone...

620
00:40:05,170 --> 00:40:08,710
who'd fall for a woman he just met?

621
00:40:12,980 --> 00:40:15,719
I feel like it's your first time
asking for a woman's number...

622
00:40:15,949 --> 00:40:18,820
after you went on
a blind date with them.

623
00:40:23,059 --> 00:40:25,130
She's a lot richer than I am.

624
00:40:25,659 --> 00:40:28,360
She comes from a better family,
and she's more competent.

625
00:40:29,059 --> 00:40:30,429
So isn't it natural?

626
00:40:31,869 --> 00:40:34,300
I'll take care of my love life
on my own.

627
00:40:36,510 --> 00:40:39,110
Wake me up
once the rice is done cooking.

628
00:40:39,440 --> 00:40:41,679
I haven't slept properly in days,
so I'm tired.

629
00:40:55,719 --> 00:40:57,090
If...

630
00:40:59,559 --> 00:41:00,659
that woman...

631
00:41:01,500 --> 00:41:02,869
didn't have any money,

632
00:41:03,400 --> 00:41:06,239
didn't come from a very good family,

633
00:41:07,239 --> 00:41:09,239
and wasn't competent at all,

634
00:41:10,070 --> 00:41:13,179
you surely wouldn't have
liked her, right?

635
00:41:16,579 --> 00:41:17,579
Director Do?

636
00:41:20,449 --> 00:41:21,619
Director Do.

637
00:41:55,050 --> 00:41:58,250
I made some mistakes,

638
00:41:58,820 --> 00:42:00,190
and I feel sorry for that.

639
00:42:01,619 --> 00:42:03,360
But I'll repay you by working hard.

640
00:42:06,159 --> 00:42:08,099
So please don't like her.

641
00:42:11,030 --> 00:42:14,699
If you like her and end up
suffering because of her,

642
00:42:16,010 --> 00:42:17,239
I'll end up hurting as well.

643
00:42:21,980 --> 00:42:22,980
My goodness.

644
00:42:26,550 --> 00:42:27,650
I'm not sleeping.

645
00:42:29,820 --> 00:42:30,949
Did you hear everything?

646
00:42:35,159 --> 00:42:37,429
How are you so simple-minded?

647
00:42:37,989 --> 00:42:41,030
Who falls asleep that fast?

648
00:42:41,929 --> 00:42:42,969
I mean...

649
00:42:43,699 --> 00:42:46,239
You should've responded if you
were awake. Why did you stay quiet?

650
00:42:46,570 --> 00:42:49,440
I was on the brink of
falling asleep.

651
00:42:51,840 --> 00:42:54,110
By the way, are you sick?

652
00:42:55,179 --> 00:42:56,650
I think I heard you say...

653
00:42:57,480 --> 00:42:59,880
that it hurts or something.

654
00:43:02,079 --> 00:43:05,789
My wrist... It really hurts.

655
00:43:05,789 --> 00:43:09,360
I wiped all the plates,
and now my wrist is killing me.

656
00:43:09,659 --> 00:43:12,360
Gosh, I should dip it in warm water.

657
00:43:20,369 --> 00:43:23,309
You know what Veronica Park
looks like, right?

658
00:43:26,380 --> 00:43:27,480
Do you not know?

659
00:43:28,510 --> 00:43:31,110
Well... Yes, I know.

660
00:43:36,650 --> 00:43:37,690
Is she pretty?

661
00:43:39,920 --> 00:43:41,119
What if she is?

662
00:43:41,219 --> 00:43:42,760
Is she pretty or not?

663
00:43:45,190 --> 00:43:48,130
If I tell him that she's pretty,
he'll end up liking her even more.

664
00:43:48,460 --> 00:43:49,500
Can you...

665
00:43:50,130 --> 00:43:52,030
describe how she looks in detail?

666
00:43:52,739 --> 00:43:54,800
What does her eyes look like?

667
00:43:56,139 --> 00:43:57,440
What about her nose?

668
00:43:58,139 --> 00:43:59,380
And what about...

669
00:44:00,380 --> 00:44:01,539
her lips?

670
00:44:03,849 --> 00:44:04,880
Tell me.

671
00:44:09,019 --> 00:44:10,389
She has...

672
00:44:12,719 --> 00:44:13,920
average looking eyes.

673
00:44:15,989 --> 00:44:17,760
And her nose...

674
00:44:19,260 --> 00:44:20,300
Her nose...

675
00:44:21,230 --> 00:44:23,000
is also very average looking.

676
00:44:25,230 --> 00:44:26,570
And her lips...

677
00:44:32,510 --> 00:44:35,280
I guess her lips are quite decent.

678
00:44:37,380 --> 00:44:39,420
But she really is pretty.

679
00:44:40,380 --> 00:44:42,650
So many people work for her...

680
00:44:43,320 --> 00:44:45,849
just to make her look pretty.

681
00:44:46,590 --> 00:44:49,320
She has custom-made clothes...

682
00:44:49,429 --> 00:44:51,030
that compliment her physique.

683
00:44:51,530 --> 00:44:53,659
And her heels that were made
not for walking purposes,

684
00:44:53,800 --> 00:44:55,630
but for beauty...

685
00:44:55,960 --> 00:44:58,130
perfect her body line.

686
00:44:59,030 --> 00:45:00,239
More importantly,

687
00:45:01,070 --> 00:45:02,300
she owns...

688
00:45:02,599 --> 00:45:04,869
a coat that nobody else owns.

689
00:45:06,880 --> 00:45:08,940
The threads on that coat
were first planted with money,

690
00:45:08,940 --> 00:45:10,550
then sewn with her parents,

691
00:45:11,349 --> 00:45:14,519
and is laminated with competence.
It's called the coat of confidence.

692
00:45:16,219 --> 00:45:17,590
It's an invisible coat,

693
00:45:18,420 --> 00:45:20,619
but anyone can see it.

694
00:45:21,320 --> 00:45:25,989
It makes her look
confident and beautiful.

695
00:45:32,570 --> 00:45:33,900
I look like a mess, right?

696
00:45:34,400 --> 00:45:36,440
I was in an audition earlier today.

697
00:45:36,710 --> 00:45:38,909
There was a girl
with a filthy temper,

698
00:45:39,309 --> 00:45:41,309
so I didn't even have time
to put on lipstick.

699
00:45:43,710 --> 00:45:45,579
You didn't have time
to put on lipstick,

700
00:45:46,679 --> 00:45:47,920
but it's on your teeth.

701
00:45:51,289 --> 00:45:53,489
I feel hungry all of a sudden.

702
00:46:00,300 --> 00:46:04,570
Sim Hae Yong asked me to come,
but Gi Dae Ju tells me not to.

703
00:46:05,630 --> 00:46:07,769
It's funny how your company works.

704
00:46:08,800 --> 00:46:12,039
I wonder who's on whose side.

705
00:46:13,639 --> 00:46:14,940
Please do me a favor.

706
00:46:15,909 --> 00:46:17,780
I have a friend who's like my wife.

707
00:46:19,619 --> 00:46:22,320
So you're asking me a favor
for your wife?

708
00:46:22,519 --> 00:46:24,190
How dare you!

709
00:46:24,190 --> 00:46:26,119
Are you thinking of saying yes,
only if I meet up with you?

710
00:46:26,519 --> 00:46:27,989
Is that it?

711
00:46:28,489 --> 00:46:30,929
You come to see me only when
you have a favor to ask me.

712
00:46:30,929 --> 00:46:32,630
You're the one who's being mean.

713
00:46:32,630 --> 00:46:35,300
Don't you think I'm using it
as an excuse to see you?

714
00:46:35,760 --> 00:46:38,429
I don't know why I'm being
so thoughtless...

715
00:46:38,699 --> 00:46:40,900
every time I see you.

716
00:46:43,340 --> 00:46:45,070
- 6 o'clock.
- 6 o'clock?

717
00:46:45,769 --> 00:46:48,139
Now that the alarm went off,

718
00:46:48,510 --> 00:46:50,780
shall we begin our love story now?

719
00:46:51,880 --> 00:46:52,920
President Park.

720
00:46:55,449 --> 00:46:56,489
Hello, ma'am.

721
00:46:59,050 --> 00:47:02,159
Do you even own this restaurant?

722
00:47:02,260 --> 00:47:04,190
That sounds so disappointing.

723
00:47:05,090 --> 00:47:08,530
I own this whole building.

724
00:47:10,500 --> 00:47:11,900
Then let's eat somewhere else.

725
00:47:12,500 --> 00:47:15,239
If you eat here,
the employees will be very tired.

726
00:47:15,969 --> 00:47:18,769
If we eat somewhere else,
I will be tired.

727
00:47:19,210 --> 00:47:21,139
I know a good sushi
restaurant near here.

728
00:47:21,579 --> 00:47:23,409
And the price is reasonable...

729
00:47:23,409 --> 00:47:25,150
so I can pay with my own card.

730
00:47:25,579 --> 00:47:29,519
You say that it's not good
in a very positive way.

731
00:47:29,889 --> 00:47:33,119
Everything tastes good as long
as I eat it with someone I like.

732
00:47:34,119 --> 00:47:38,090
Are you saying that you like me...

733
00:47:38,090 --> 00:47:39,900
in a coy way?

734
00:47:40,699 --> 00:47:41,860
It was a subjunctive.

735
00:47:42,559 --> 00:47:46,639
If I eat something
with someone I like...

736
00:47:47,670 --> 00:47:50,869
You'll see. I'll make
that subjunctive...

737
00:47:50,869 --> 00:47:53,039
into a present progressive.

738
00:47:53,909 --> 00:47:54,980
Let's go!

739
00:48:03,849 --> 00:48:04,920
Director Do.

740
00:48:05,690 --> 00:48:08,389
There were a hair band
and a sewing kit in the bathroom.

741
00:48:08,820 --> 00:48:11,889
I didn't think you'd need them,
so I took them.

742
00:48:13,159 --> 00:48:14,260
Thank you.

743
00:48:19,429 --> 00:48:20,769
Gosh, it's all on my shirt.

744
00:48:25,769 --> 00:48:26,840
Are you asleep?

745
00:48:28,610 --> 00:48:30,309
Are you sleepy again?

746
00:48:37,920 --> 00:48:39,489
Sleep in the room.

747
00:48:43,289 --> 00:48:44,829
I guess he's asleep.

748
00:48:48,500 --> 00:48:49,769
I should straighten his neck.

749
00:49:15,719 --> 00:49:16,860
I can see you.

750
00:49:18,130 --> 00:49:19,190
What?

751
00:49:19,489 --> 00:49:20,559
In my dream,

752
00:49:22,730 --> 00:49:24,199
I can see everything.

753
00:49:24,699 --> 00:49:27,070
This isn't a dream.

754
00:49:30,710 --> 00:49:31,710
You're pretty.

755
00:49:35,480 --> 00:49:37,449
Am I pretty?

756
00:49:39,380 --> 00:49:41,480
Yes. You're pretty.

757
00:49:44,550 --> 00:49:46,090
Even though I have no money?

758
00:49:49,929 --> 00:49:51,190
Even though I don't own a building?

759
00:49:57,730 --> 00:50:00,969
Even though I don't have parents?

760
00:50:08,139 --> 00:50:09,710
I wish it wasn't a dream.

761
00:50:18,349 --> 00:50:19,349
What?

762
00:50:20,190 --> 00:50:21,260
This isn't a dream?

763
00:50:23,289 --> 00:50:24,389
Of course not.

764
00:50:25,429 --> 00:50:27,599
How could you be so simple-minded?

765
00:50:28,030 --> 00:50:30,530
How could you start
dreaming so soon?

766
00:50:32,030 --> 00:50:33,070
Well...

767
00:50:33,969 --> 00:50:35,199
I thought...

768
00:50:36,469 --> 00:50:38,269
you were Veronica.

769
00:50:39,269 --> 00:50:41,409
It's me, Secretary Jeong.

770
00:50:42,880 --> 00:50:44,849
You don't even know
how Veronica looks like.

771
00:50:45,610 --> 00:50:48,320
Well... I know that.

772
00:50:50,119 --> 00:50:54,389
I just felt that way
for the time being.

773
00:50:56,059 --> 00:50:58,289
I'll be here at eight
tomorrow morning.

774
00:50:58,829 --> 00:50:59,900
Bye.

775
00:51:02,659 --> 00:51:03,699
Don't go.

776
00:51:12,539 --> 00:51:13,579
Sleep over.

777
00:51:21,579 --> 00:51:24,920
I'll go. You can stay here.

778
00:51:28,460 --> 00:51:30,989
Gosh, no. You don't
have to do that for me.

779
00:51:31,730 --> 00:51:33,559
For you? You think?

780
00:51:34,559 --> 00:51:38,099
This is just about marginal utility.

781
00:51:38,130 --> 00:51:41,400
I get to sleep here all the time,
but this is your first time.

782
00:51:41,400 --> 00:51:44,539
So it will create
even more satisfaction.

783
00:51:44,539 --> 00:51:45,610
It's all about economics.

784
00:51:52,380 --> 00:51:53,380
Stand up.

785
00:52:00,460 --> 00:52:01,789
Where was it?

786
00:52:13,369 --> 00:52:14,639
What are you doing?

787
00:52:15,039 --> 00:52:17,869
Secretary Jeong, you were
talking about...

788
00:52:18,409 --> 00:52:19,980
some coat of confidence
earlier today.

789
00:52:20,610 --> 00:52:21,679
This is it.

790
00:52:23,750 --> 00:52:26,349
Secretary Jeong, I want you
to stay here a few days...

791
00:52:26,349 --> 00:52:27,579
wearing that coat.

792
00:52:29,179 --> 00:52:31,920
This isn't about
consideration at all.

793
00:52:31,920 --> 00:52:33,989
I'm just doing this for me.

794
00:52:34,789 --> 00:52:37,059
If you lose confidence
before the stockholders' meeting,

795
00:52:37,659 --> 00:52:39,900
it will just depress me.

796
00:52:42,300 --> 00:52:44,599
The spa opens at 10,

797
00:52:44,630 --> 00:52:46,670
and the breakfast buffet
opens at six.

798
00:52:50,309 --> 00:52:52,909
Make sure to have the door locked.

799
00:53:09,929 --> 00:53:12,230
I thought
Secretary Jeong was coming.

800
00:53:12,530 --> 00:53:15,000
She will stay at the hotel
for the time being.

801
00:53:16,699 --> 00:53:17,869
Let's go home.

802
00:53:18,099 --> 00:53:19,369
Yes, sir.

803
00:53:39,250 --> 00:53:42,119
I'm Jeong Gal Hee who's
staying in a suite.

804
00:53:44,989 --> 00:53:46,059
Yes, you're pretty.

805
00:53:52,530 --> 00:53:54,769
I guess I did become prettier.

806
00:53:55,469 --> 00:53:57,170
As if I actually became her.

807
00:53:59,539 --> 00:54:00,710
I thought...

808
00:54:02,110 --> 00:54:04,579
you were Veronica.

809
00:54:05,880 --> 00:54:07,579
That can't be right.

810
00:54:08,480 --> 00:54:10,389
Sure. That's not true.

811
00:54:17,489 --> 00:54:19,489
This is what it feels like...

812
00:54:20,099 --> 00:54:21,360
to look down from above.

813
00:54:23,769 --> 00:54:24,769
It's good.

814
00:54:31,739 --> 00:54:36,110
(2 weeks later, the day of
TnT Mobile's stockholders' meeting)

815
00:54:36,110 --> 00:54:38,079
I guess we picked the wrong day.

816
00:54:38,179 --> 00:54:40,179
Or maybe, we picked the perfect day.

817
00:54:48,289 --> 00:54:49,519
Why do you look so intimidated?

818
00:54:50,190 --> 00:54:51,329
No, I'm not.

819
00:54:52,130 --> 00:54:55,199
I was just hoping the stockholders'
meeting would be canceled.

820
00:54:56,030 --> 00:54:57,699
Let's not bet on it.

821
00:54:57,699 --> 00:55:01,000
If it could be cancelled, they
wouldn't even have started it.

822
00:55:10,480 --> 00:55:12,179
- What are you doing?
- Wait.

823
00:55:12,909 --> 00:55:15,050
Your heart is beating too fast.

824
00:55:16,280 --> 00:55:17,949
Maybe you should have taken
an antihypertensive drug.

825
00:55:18,250 --> 00:55:20,360
Don't be ridiculous.

826
00:55:20,360 --> 00:55:21,389
I just...

827
00:55:21,659 --> 00:55:24,630
got a bit scared
because I might break the record...

828
00:55:24,630 --> 00:55:26,800
of the number of faceless people
I see today.

829
00:55:28,400 --> 00:55:29,559
How great is that?

830
00:55:30,130 --> 00:55:31,170
What is?

831
00:55:31,670 --> 00:55:33,699
Many people get nervous on stage...

832
00:55:33,699 --> 00:55:35,369
and close their eyes.

833
00:55:35,769 --> 00:55:38,110
But you can't see any of the faces.

834
00:55:39,570 --> 00:55:42,610
Just look at me on the stage.

835
00:55:42,840 --> 00:55:43,880
I'm a stakeholder too...

836
00:55:44,880 --> 00:55:47,079
with 10 shares of the company,
after all.

837
00:55:48,050 --> 00:55:49,150
Only 10?

838
00:55:50,389 --> 00:55:51,389
Shall we?

839
00:55:51,489 --> 00:55:52,650
Wait a second.

840
00:56:02,300 --> 00:56:04,730
I'll let you borrow my coat.

841
00:56:04,929 --> 00:56:06,400
Make sure to give it back to me
after you use it.

842
00:56:15,610 --> 00:56:17,179
Hey, hey, hey.

843
00:56:17,579 --> 00:56:20,820
There are a lot less people
than I thought.

844
00:56:21,380 --> 00:56:22,920
It's starting at two.

845
00:56:22,920 --> 00:56:25,889
Unless someone who has
over 100,000 shares shows up,

846
00:56:25,889 --> 00:56:27,389
the meeting might be canceled.

847
00:56:30,929 --> 00:56:34,000
That woman has to come.

848
00:56:34,929 --> 00:56:38,099
The board of directors believes that
conniving assault...

849
00:56:38,530 --> 00:56:41,269
in the workplace
is an irresponsible action...

850
00:56:41,670 --> 00:56:43,300
that encourages abuse of power...

851
00:56:43,300 --> 00:56:45,369
and depresses
the morale of the employees.

852
00:56:45,769 --> 00:56:47,809
Therefore, we suggest the
resignation of Director Do Min Ik...

853
00:56:47,809 --> 00:56:50,650
for the agenda
of today's stockholders' meeting.

854
00:56:51,650 --> 00:56:52,679
Sir.

855
00:56:52,909 --> 00:56:55,050
(TnT Mobile
Extraordinary Stockholders' Meeting)

856
00:56:56,550 --> 00:56:57,989
Yes, please go ahead.

857
00:57:00,619 --> 00:57:04,559
I would like to hear Director Do's
stance regarding the matter.

858
00:57:14,239 --> 00:57:15,739
This is unfair.

859
00:57:17,139 --> 00:57:18,309
I second the motion.

860
00:57:31,219 --> 00:57:32,289
Ma'am.

861
00:57:32,920 --> 00:57:33,989
Good to see you here.

862
00:57:34,989 --> 00:57:36,260
How did you...

863
00:57:36,460 --> 00:57:39,059
It seemed like something fun was
going on in this company.

864
00:57:39,059 --> 00:57:41,000
So I came to watch the fun.

865
00:57:41,630 --> 00:57:42,730
Oh, no.

866
00:57:43,500 --> 00:57:46,300
If he sees her...

867
00:57:47,139 --> 00:57:48,869
See whom?

868
00:57:50,369 --> 00:57:51,369
Well...

869
00:57:54,940 --> 00:57:57,880
I know this could sound weird,

870
00:57:58,110 --> 00:57:59,750
but if you're here just for fun,

871
00:58:00,280 --> 00:58:01,780
could you please just leave?

872
00:58:03,019 --> 00:58:04,849
For you, it might be
just a fun thing to watch.

873
00:58:04,849 --> 00:58:07,059
But my life is on the line.

874
00:58:07,260 --> 00:58:08,789
It really sounds weird...

875
00:58:08,789 --> 00:58:10,559
and I don't want to leave.

876
00:58:11,429 --> 00:58:13,059
Besides,

877
00:58:13,230 --> 00:58:16,730
how many times have I told you
that you have to use people?

878
00:58:16,929 --> 00:58:19,730
I have no idea
how many shares you have,

879
00:58:19,730 --> 00:58:22,139
if you want to help your boss,

880
00:58:22,139 --> 00:58:24,539
or if you want to take down
your boss.

881
00:58:25,440 --> 00:58:28,309
But whatever it is, do you think
you have enough votes for it?

882
00:58:29,579 --> 00:58:30,610
I, on the other hand,

883
00:58:31,079 --> 00:58:34,519
can cut off your boss' neck
and put it back...

884
00:58:35,349 --> 00:58:37,219
with just one finger.

885
00:58:37,590 --> 00:58:40,719
I can twist and squeeze his neck.

886
00:58:40,820 --> 00:58:41,920
I can do anything I want.

887
00:58:44,429 --> 00:58:45,460
What do you say?

888
00:58:46,159 --> 00:58:47,199
Do you still want me to leave?

889
00:58:47,400 --> 00:58:50,030
As the stakeholders suggested,

890
00:58:50,530 --> 00:58:53,469
we're going to hear
Director Do Min Ik's stance.

891
00:59:02,210 --> 00:59:03,380
Should I leave?

892
00:59:42,579 --> 00:59:43,579
I can see faces.
